import { Image } from "@chakra-ui/image";
import { Box, Flex, Heading, Text } from "@chakra-ui/layout";
import Nav from "../components/Nav";
import { Button } from "@chakra-ui/button";


export default function QuemSomos() {
    
    return(
        <Box height="100%" backgroundcolor="red">
            <Nav/>
            <Box position="relative" mt="45px" maxW="1367px" >
                <Flex justifyContent="center" >
                    <Heading
                    fontWeight="bold"
                    fontSize="26px"
                    lineHeight="30px"
                    color="#454545"
                    >
                        Quem somos
                    </Heading>
                    <Text
                    fontWeight="500"
                    fontSize="18px"
                    lineHeight="21px"
                    color="#454545"
                    >
                        Conheça a equipe por trás da produção da plataforma GoTokens.
                    </Text>
                </Flex>
            </Box>
        </Box>
    );
}
